<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à </span></b><font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US">The scope of the definition of mental patients in the Mental Health Act</span></b><span lang="EN-US"> will be narrowed down and when charging the health insurance benefit in the case of simple psychological counseling without drug prescription, the name of mental illness will not be indicated to eliminate the bias against mental illness and to encourage people to use the psychological medical service.</span></font><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> <o:p></o:p></span></b></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 5pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span></span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.8pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 28.8pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à “</span></b><font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US">Mental Health Checkups by Life Cycle” for the whole nation</span></b><span lang="EN-US"> will be conducted from 2013 in order to check individual mental health status and encourage people with mental problem to receive early treatment.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23.3pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 27.3pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><main details=""><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></main></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23.3pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 27.3pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à </span></b><font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US">The education and specialized counseling system</span></b><span lang="EN-US"> will be expanded so that stress and depression, etc. can be well handled at workplaces and schools.</span></font><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.6pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 28.6pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><main details=""><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></main></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -10pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 10pt; vertical-align: baseline; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à Through psychological support for those who attempt suicide, bereaved families and </span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">people around them who visit the emergency room, the spread of suicide will be blocked and the youth and elderly suicide prevention system will be established in connection with schools and local welfare organizations.<b> </b></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.5pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 28.5pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><main details=""><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></main></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -27.6pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 31.6pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à In order for those who are addicted to the internet, gambling, alcohol and drug</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> to use professional treatment service more easily and to be rehabilitated, related infrastructure and psychological support for their families will be strengthened.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23.1pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 27.1pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><main details=""><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></main></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23.1pt; margin: 0cm 4pt 0pt 27.1pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font size="2"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">¡à </span></b><span lang="EN-US"><font color="#000000">The title of Mental Health Act will be revised to Mental Health Improvement Act and the Mental Health Center will be changed to the Mental Health Improvement Center. To reinforce the functions of mental health policy research and development, the National Mental Health Research Institute will be newly established.</font></span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; letter-spacing: -0.4pt; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> </span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
</td>
