</table>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">¡à Ministry of Health and Welfare announced that </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">it will narrow down the scope of the definition of the mental health status and conduct mental screening for the all Koreans from 2013. (</span><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">the mental health checkups by life cycle will be conducted to check individual mental health status for the whole nation from 2013, narrowing down the scope of the definition of the mental patient in Mental Health Act.)<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.5pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û When charging the health insurance benefit for simple counseling by a psychiatrist, the name of mental illness will not be indicated but the charging will be done under the name of “general counseling.”<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.1pt">
<font size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">¡Û The mental health control system at schools and workplaces for students and workers will be reinforced and the suicide prevention system will be also established for the high risk group such as the elderly living </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">alone</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000"> those who attempt suicide and people around them. <o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Ministry of Health and Welfare <span style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">(Minister Rim, Chae Min) recognized the seriousness of the problem that 14.4% of adults aged 18 and older (5.19 million people) suffer mental illness once or more in their lives as the result of the 2011 mental illness status survey showed and announced the Comprehensive Plan for Mental Health Improvement that contains such significance.*</span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -36.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* It was put on the agenda for the 121<sup>st</sup> National Policy Coordination Meeting (22 June 2012) chaired by Prime Minister. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊱</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"> The scope of the definition of the mental patient will be narrowed down and the accessibility to psychiatry will be improved. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></b></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Mental patient will be defined as “someone recognized by a psychiatrist as unable to carry out every day social activities from among those with mental illness.”<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û In this regard, the scope of the definition of the mental patient in Mental Health Act will be narrowed down to the severe patient that requires hospitalization treatment<s>, etc.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></s></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The definition of the mental patient under the current Mental Health Act includes those who have had simple counseling with a psychiatrist without considering the severity level of the patient’s condition.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -36.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">* <span style="letter-spacing: -0.6pt">(</span></span><span lang="EN-US">Article 3 of Mental Health Act) Mental patient refers to one with mental illness (including organic mental illness), character disorder, and other non-mental illness disorder such as alcoholism and drug addict. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.9pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.9pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The health insurance benefit is charged in the case of simple counseling without medication prescription, it can be done under the title of “general counseling” without the name of mental illness being indicated. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.9pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.9pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Those suffering light mental illness who don’t have problems with living everyday lives by taking counseling and medication will be excluded from the scope of the definition of the mental patient so that they will be protected from irrational social discrimination. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û This will get rid of social stigma that used to affect those with just a record of receiving psychological counseling without medication prescription, thus, enhancing the accessibility to a psychiatrist by those who are suspected of having mental illness.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font color="#000000"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Implementation of Mental Health Checkups by Life Cycle </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The mental health</font><span style="color: red"> test</span><font color="#000000"> by life cycle will be conducted twice for preschoolers and elementary school students, once for middle school and high school students </font><span style="color: red">each</span><font color="#000000">, three times for those in 20s and twice </font><span style="color: red">in each decade beyond that</span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The checkups for those in their 20s, which is the highest risk group and experience going to school of advanced education, employment and joining the military service, etc. will be carried out more than other age groups- three times. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">¡Û Mental Health Checkups will be run in a way that the National Health Insurance Corporation will send the checkup tool to individuals via mail and individuals will fill up the survey as self-entry (parents will fill in the form for preschoolers) and send it back to the Corporation for assessment. <o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.5pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Ministry of Health and Welfare expects that people will be able to check their own mental health status themselves through the checkups and early treatment will be made possible such as the mental health service for the risk group.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p align="left" class="a" style="text-align: left; line-height: 50%; text-indent: -32.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.3pt; word-break: keep-all">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="a" style="text-align: left; line-height: 50%; text-indent: -32.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.3pt; word-break: keep-all">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊳</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> Establishment of Workplace- and School-based Mental Health Improvement System</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The Mental Health Improvement Program will be expanded to prevent and relieve workers’ stress and depression, etc. for small- and medium-sized companies and petty businesses.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The program of mental health support for workers to prevent and relieve stress and depression, etc. will be provided to small- and medium- sized companies in connection with a private organization. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -32.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The work-related stress control program will be offered to petty businesses in cooperation with Korea Occupational Safety &amp; Health Agency, Korea Labor Welfare Corporation and Mental Health Center. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -32.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The psychological test and specialized counseling service will be expanded at public organizations with high work-related stress such as fire station, and police station, etc. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.7pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The counseling function within school to tackle students’ mental health problems resulting from school violence, suicide, and increased study burden, etc. will be reinforced.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -10pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û Specialized personnel will be secured such as specialized counselor and clinical counselor, etc. at “Wee Center”, etc. to strengthen the function of counseling for students in the high risk group. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û When counseling by expert or treatment is required, the support will be provided through the Mental Health Center and when needed, a mental medical institution will be linked for the service or treatment. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p align="left" class="a" style="text-align: left; line-height: 50%; text-indent: -32.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.3pt; word-break: keep-all">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="a" style="text-align: left; line-height: 50%; text-indent: -32.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.3pt; word-break: keep-all">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊴</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> Establishment of Early Intervention System for Suicide Prevention </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The suicide prevention system will be established that links psychological treatment and social welfare service for those who have attempted suicide that visit the emergency room.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">¡Û Those who attempt suicide will be </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">connected to treatment in mental clinic first, and then </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">provided with afterwards psychological support through the mental health center in their areas <o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<font size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">¡à Additional suicide prevention system will be prepared to deal with psychological shock, and depression, etc. </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">for</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000"> </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">the</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000"> bereaved families and people around suffer after someone commits suicide. <o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û When a suicide occurs, a psychological test will be conducted through the mental health center and when needed, a case control, psychological consulting and psychological treatment will be linked.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à For the elderly living alone, a vulnerable class, helpers and visiting nurses will be trained to find suicide risks among them.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û A system will be established to provide a depression test and psychological support service through the mental health center when abnormal signs are found such as suicide attempt. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à The life-respecting education will be strengthened in the middle and high school curriculum and for schools of which a student has committed suicide or attempted one, the psychological test and counseling service will be provided through the mental health center and Wee center.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Ministry of Health and Welfare informed that it will minimize suicide attempts by intervening in for the high risk groups such as those who have attempted suicide, bereaved families and people around them through such measures..<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font color="#000000"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊵</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"> Improvement of Addiction Prevention System </span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.5pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Standard counseling and treatment guidelines regarding the internet and gambling addiction will be prepared and distributed to counseling agencies and a training course for personnel specialized in addiction counseling in linkage with the treatment guideline will be open and run. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à A comprehensive deliverance system including medical treatment, social welfare and correction service will be prepared in cooperation with related organizations for alcoholics.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -36.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -44.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 44.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* National Mental Hospital, Alcoholic Counseling Center, rehabilitation facilities for the elderly living alone, the police and shelters <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -44.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 44.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -32.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û Drinking and the sales of alcoholic beverage at some public facilities will be limited and the restraint on alcoholic beverage advertisements will be reinforced as well. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -23pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à For drug addiction, Ministry of Health and Welfare will prepare measures to facilitate the collaboration with related organizations such as Ministry of Justice and Food and Drug Agency, etc. so that treatment and rehabilitation can be achieved smoothly.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -22.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">¡à Specialized counseling support will be expanded for family members of the addicted who are suffering depression and mental trauma through the mental health center and agencies designed to deal with addition at each ministry.<o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊶</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> Establishment of Effective Hospitalization Treatment System<o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">¡à The application of the health insurance fee* will be run as a pilot program for a certain period of time for severe mental patients who are being hospitalized into mental medical institutions for the first time.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -30.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û By applying the health insurance fee, it will be encouraged to make the concentrated treatment at an early phase of hospitalization and early discharge possible. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -36.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: -44.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 44.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* Through a pilot program in some areas, the effectiveness of treatment and economic feasibility will be evaluated. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -32.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û After discharge, the support will be made for them to be able to get a job and adjust to the society by linking them with the mental health center and social integration facilities. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -32.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -24.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à It also added that it is anticipated that by providing the concentrated treatment for severe mental patients under the health insurance fee at an early phase of their hospitalization, the effectiveness of treatment and the possibility of returning to the society will be enhanced.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><span style="letter-spacing: -0.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -24.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font color="#000000"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'">󰊷</span></b><b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"> Strengthening of the Public Mental Health Infrastructure </span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">¡à </span><span lang="EN-US">The title of Mental Health Act will be revised to Mental Health Improvement Act and the Mental Health Center will be changed to the Mental Health Improvement Center. To reinforce the functions of mental health policy research and development, the National Mental Health Research Institute will be newly established. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -32.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The contents of the Mental Health Improvement Act will be revised by moving its focus from the hospitalization and treatment of severe mental patients to the mental health improvement and early discovery and treatment of mental illness for all the public. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -32.4pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.4pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -30.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30.3pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.03">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û By reinforcing the capacity of the Mental Health Improvement Center in the metropolitan area to carry out a systemic mental health improvement program, its leadership* for local-level centers will be established.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -44.7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 44.7pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* Evaluation, education and business guidelines, etc. for the mental health centers in the its district <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">- Ways to make mental health improvement programs available considering the uniqueness of each area such as major mental health problems in the concerned areas will be prepared. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -35.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 35.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin">¡à Background of the Establishment of the Comprehensive Plan </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></font></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; vertical-align: baseline">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: black; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ±¼¸²; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -23.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.2pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à This Comprehensive Plan for Mental Health Improvement has been prepared to improve problems of the negative notion, biased view and discrimination against mental illness, the wide spread of mental illnesses such as depression, the tendency of long-term hospitalization for severe mental patients and the steady increase of the suicide rates. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000">¡Û Early </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; color: red; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">detection</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font color="#000000"> and treatment of mental illness is an indispensable requisite for preventing the decrease of the rate of treatment resulting from the illness becoming chronic and the sharp increase of treatment cost. <o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -31.1pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.1pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -32.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 32.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û The ministry said that preventive and aggressive control of mental health problems is very important as it will raise the value of individuals’ lives and secure human resources with future competitiveness.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -43.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 43.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* Social cost is incurred such as the decline of productivity, absence, sick leave and early retirement due to mental illness and its amount is around two to three times greater than the medical expenditure (OECD Policy Report, 2008).<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -31.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.6pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡à Ministry of Health and Welfare said that it is setting up practical policy measures to create healthy families by linking health and welfare for the elderly living alone, Tuberculosis, mental health, development disorder and dementia. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -24.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24.3pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -30pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 30pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">¡Û This plan was prepared in line with such efforts and the Ministry said it will continue to prepare measures by each case to make lives of all the people more valuable and create a healthier society. <o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -22.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 22.8pt">
<a name="_GoBack"></a><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="a" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: -43.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 43.8pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font size="2"><font color="#000000">* Comprehensive support plan for the elderly living alone (announced on 11 May), National TB control reinforcement plan (announced on 18 June)<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></p></td>
